{"tid":1572351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"報數埋班後，我諗到進階救人法","createTime":"2019-09-15T16:03:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T17:04:33.000Z","uid":264149,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7d999e553d0f0069eb227704efb7d6471fda184d","tid":1572351,"uid":264149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:03:31.000Z","msg":"首先畀返credit兩位巴打同其他諗計嘅手足先，<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1571314/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1571314/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1569278/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1569278/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n但愚見認爲當場嘈雜混亂，等齊報數可能都應該唔夠快，<strong>電光火石<span style=\"color: green;\"></span></strong>之間手足可能已經被人打咗、拖咗、拉咗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我提議：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">開遮！！！！</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">開遮！！！！</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">開遮！！！！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n橫掂都係要開遮 C Bird，<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />何不以開遮爲記，又易認，又唔怕嘈叫唔到手足。<br />\n<br />\n我怕自己諗得唔夠周全，野人獻曝其實777咗，希望集思廣益下，有錯漏隨便屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b5723f744190e0fc6f4dab7bffaed03029e1f40","tid":1572351,"uid":264149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:04:02.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"d092dbe40db8a94db16368953aaeee096b910435","tid":1572351,"uid":264149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:05:39.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"2c8d8b67c6f5eedfcc42b4f3bf169bcd80ac8a19","tid":1572351,"uid":107898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:18:31.000Z","msg":"做得好 有改進 能完善<br />\n行動最實際<br />\n對比人數<br />\n掩護重要啲"},{"pid":"c64321e3ae5ac43d1a04d61636d20f67b7f91ba3","tid":1572351,"uid":119895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:20:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"91cc7faf4cc9930d82eb1089ae3eec34053a8a91","tid":1572351,"uid":113155,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:20:54.000Z","msg":"開遮咪少咗隻手又少咗件武器囉"},{"pid":"155b6afb104a02c48cd7e00bd7237008fd6c7269","tid":1572351,"uid":15259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:22:49.000Z","msg":"只有一個方法可以有效打擊藍屍<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1570141\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1570141</a>"},{"pid":"5f5dbe62378cf1574beadcfb0205be1ddbda5fb9","tid":1572351,"uid":264149,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"91cc7faf4cc9930d82eb1089ae3eec34053a8a91","tid":1572351,"uid":113155,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:20:54.000Z","msg":"開遮咪少咗隻手又少咗件武器囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:31:10.000Z","msg":"我覺得係帶頭嗰個開一把遮，大家見遮就迅速埋位一齊出勳"},{"pid":"e7d285c4f62f66714dad4c01927a8a32ffefb47f","tid":1572351,"uid":264149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:31:49.000Z","msg":"自推3"},{"pid":"fc32c67d2a9e99d7cdf24b6cc556ac2501959d88","tid":1572351,"uid":264149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:50:15.000Z","msg":"喺唔怕嘈又夠配合行動以外，想補充幾個理念：<br />\n<br />\n1. （回應有巴打話開遮少咗隻手）一個開遮好夠，其餘大家一齊去遮底開始行動/認住把遮<br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: green;\">開遮門檻低過出手，但又夠曬「前線」，做成風氣可以喺商場/街邊呢啲場景拉未夠深黃嘅人落水，令佢地有勇武feel或經驗，逐步升呢</span>，同時適合女仔所以係<span style=\"color: violet;\">分工</span>嚟嘅<br />\n<br />\n3. 知道有遮，手足會<strong>盡興</strong>啲<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論，有錯請屌，或者加多啲idea"},{"pid":"2e3efae388742d47cfab1e37e998d6d10db7c755","tid":1572351,"uid":107898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fc32c67d2a9e99d7cdf24b6cc556ac2501959d88","tid":1572351,"uid":264149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:50:15.000Z","msg":"喺唔怕嘈又夠配合行動以外，想補充幾個理念：<br />\n<br />\n1. （回應有巴打話開遮少咗隻手）一個開遮好夠，其餘大家一齊去遮底開始行動/認住把遮<br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: green;\">開遮門檻低過出手，但又夠曬「前線」，做成風氣可以喺商場/街邊呢啲場景拉未夠深黃嘅人落水，令佢地有勇武feel或經驗，逐步升呢</span>，同時適合女仔所以係<span style=\"color: violet;\">分工</span>嚟嘅<br />\n<br />\n3. 知道有遮，手足會<strong>盡興</strong>啲<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論，有錯請屌，或者加多啲idea"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:56:35.000Z","msg":"啱呀，大家有分工<br />\n反正把遮只能做矛不能砍<br />\n仲要喺長遮先喺<br />\n結果有遮而又唔能落手既就開遮<br />\n所以未必影響落手既手足<br />\n<br />\n另外，遮陣可以隔離做到落單"},{"pid":"ad7020c2d346ea8930b7a271739a0d96a33bc83b","tid":1572351,"uid":135623,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"91cc7faf4cc9930d82eb1089ae3eec34053a8a91","tid":1572351,"uid":113155,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:20:54.000Z","msg":"開遮咪少咗隻手又少咗件武器囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:57:49.000Z","msg":"唔係個個都會打架嘛"},{"pid":"aed220ffa527c379e019580f04af474656a647d8","tid":1572351,"uid":107898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:59:40.000Z","msg":"開遮速度快過數夠人<br />\n就算開遮之後冇人出手<br />\n都可做盾擋一擋<br />\n<br />\n相反唔夠人就企咗喺度"},{"pid":"e394473cdc6742473d2e9106e224d563ca0076b1","tid":1572351,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:01:31.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n[品葱轉載] [文宣戰術] 教你如何宣傳反共，緊貼現在熱門事件。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ebhFbS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ebhFbS</a>"},{"pid":"7903f1de0b5de74d76aa7b39562adaa9d9d6440b","tid":1572351,"uid":264149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:07:30.000Z","msg":"自推4"},{"pid":"cd97dc2ef210b73eda9b8bd5629fd955e0ec4e3c","tid":1572351,"uid":264149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:23:47.000Z","msg":"自推5"},{"pid":"e79624ee2f946ba25ffb304c629f4c8d9633a751","tid":1572351,"uid":264149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:47:23.000Z","msg":"自推6"},{"pid":"f41263c6e26